d9870e8f-0 bMtwqF"><div class="sc-c83e4c92-0 cFULRC"><a href="/essays/what-should-econ-101-courses-teach-students-today"><div class="sc-59baed0b-9 nvsYc"><div type="essay" class="sc-4c9ef492-2 fycPaJ"><img alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/19da7ff8-2a47-4bf6-a2e3-9f6b35241ec9/final-essay-gettyimages-1360865383.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/19da7ff8-2a47-4bf6-a2e3-9f6b35241ec9/final-essay-gettyimages-1360865383.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/19da7ff8-2a47-4bf6-a2e3-9f6b35241ec9/final-essay-gettyimages-1360865383.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/19da7ff8-2a47-4bf6-a2e3-9f6b35241ec9/final-essay-gettyimages-1360865383.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/19da7ff8-2a47-4bf6-a2e3-9f6b35241ec9/final-essay-gettyimages-1360865383.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/19da7ff8-2a47-4bf6-a2e3-9f6b35241ec9/final-essay-gettyimages-1360865383.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/19da7ff8-2a47-4bf6-a2e3-9f6b35241ec9/final-essay-gettyimages-1360865383.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/19da7ff8-2a47-4bf6-a2e3-9f6b35241ec9/final-essay-gettyimages-1360865383.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/19da7ff8-2a47-4bf6-a2e3-9f6b35241ec9/final-essay-gettyimages-1360865383.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/19da7ff8-2a47-4bf6-a2e3-9f6b35241ec9/final-essay-gettyimages-1360865383.jpg?w