7","title":"Chastising little brother","slug":"japans-war-on-china-and-the-weaponisation-of-confucianism","type":"essay","audio":null,"standfirstShort":"Japan’s war on China and the weaponisation of Confucianism","standfirstLong":"Why did Japanese Confucians enthusiastically support Imperial Japan’s murderous conquest of China, the homeland of Confucius?","duration":0,"creditsShort":null,"commentsEnabled":false,"settings":{"badgeColor":null,"cardPlayIconColor":null,"alignX":"center","alignY":"center","backdropStrength":3},"tags":[],"authors":[{"id":"193621","name":"Shaun O’Dwyer"}],"image":{"url":"https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/12dbaacb-79d4-4547-889d-be4aa2a787cb/essay-aeon-header-the-kingly-way-linzhi-wang-and-shaun-o_dwyer.jpg","alt":"Black and white image of Japanese soldiers in battle gear marching with a Rising Sun Flag, superimposed with large Japanese calligraphy characters on a plain background.","height":1252,"width":2000},"primaryTopic":{"title":"Nations and empires","slug":"nations-and-empires"},"topics":[{"slug":"nations-and-empires","title":"Nations and empires"},{"slug":"war-and-peace","title":"War and peace"},{"slug":"values-beliefs","title":"Values and beliefs"}],"section":{"title":"Society","slug":"society"},"createdAt":"2024-04-08T11:39:33Z"},{"id":"7290","title":"Her blazing world","slug":"the-contradictions-that-give-life-to-margaret-cavendishs-story","type":"essay","audio":null,"standfirstShort":"The contradictions that give life to Margaret Cavendish’s story","standfirstLong":"Margaret Cavendish’s boldness and bravery set 17th-century society alight, but is she a feminist poster-girl for our times?","duration":0,"creditsShort":null,"commentsEnabled":false,"settings":{"badgeColor":null,"cardPlayIconColor":null,"alignX":"right","alignY":"center","backdropStrength":3},"tags":[],"authors":[{"id":"193699","name":"Francesca Peacock"}],"image":{"url":"https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/b164b2ac-1ac9-40ca-8587-2039b277439c/cavendish-by-lely-essay.